<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Graduation Ceremony Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e24aa, #ab47bc, #ba68c8);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #7b1fa2;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 250px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9800, #f57c00);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 16px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .event-details {
            background-color: #f3e5f5;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #8e24aa;
        }
        .icon-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .icon {
            color: #8e24aa;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            min-width: 24px;
        }
        .student-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #7b1fa2;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <center style="width: 100%;">
        <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 600px;">
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
                <td align="center" style="padding: 30px 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e24aa, #ab47bc, #ba68c8); text-align: center; color: #ffffff;">
                    <div style="font-size: 48px; margin: 15px 0; color: #ffd700;">
                        <svg width="70" height="70" viewBox="0 0 70 70" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
                            <path d="M56.5,25.5L35,15L13.5,25.5L35,36L56.5,25.5z" fill="#ffd700" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                            <path d="M13.5,25.5L35,36L35,15L13.5,25.5z" fill="#e6c300" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                            <circle cx="35" cy="15" r="2.5" fill="#ccac00"/>
                            <path d="M35,15L35,45" stroke="#ccac00" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                            <path d="M35,45L30,55L40,55L35,45z" fill="#ccac00"/>
                            <path d="M30,55L30,60L40,60L40,55" fill="#ccac00"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        UNIVERSITY OF RWANDA
                    </a>
                    <p style="margin: 0;">Class of 2025 Graduation Celebration</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #ffffff;">
                    <h1 style="color: #7b1fa2; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
                        You're Invited to Celebrate
                    </h1>

                    <div class="student-name">
                        <%= studentName %>
                    </div>
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        With great pride and joy, we invite you to celebrate the academic achievements of 
                        <strong><%= studentName %></strong> at the University of Rwanda's 2025 Graduation Ceremony.
                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        This milestone represents years of dedication, hard work, and perseverance. 
                        Join us as we honor this significant accomplishment and look forward to the bright future ahead.
                    </p>

                    <div style="background-color: #f3e5f5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-left: 5px solid #8e24aa;">
                        <h2 style="color: #7b1fa2; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                            Ceremony Details
                        </h2>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #8e24aa; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#8e24aa">
                                    <path d="M19,4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5C3.9,4,3,4.9,3,6v14c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2h14c1.1,0,2-0.9,2-2V6C21,4.9,20.1,4,19,4z M19,20H5V9h14V20z"/>
                                    <rect x="7" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="11" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="15" y="11" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="7" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="11" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                    <rect x="15" y="14" width="2" height="2"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div><strong>Date:</strong> Friday, October 10, 2025</div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #8e24aa; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#8e24aa">
                                    <path d="M12,2C6.5,2,2,6.5,2,12s4.5,10,10,10s10-4.5,10-10S17.5,2,12,2z M12,20c-4.4,0-8-3.6-8-8s3.6-8,8-8s8,3.6,8,8S16.4,20,12,20z"/>
                                    <polygon points="12.5,7 11,7 11,13 16.2,16.2 17,14.9 12.5,12.2"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Time:</strong> 09:00 AM (Doors open at 08:00 AM)
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #8e24aa; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#8e24aa">
                                    <path d="M12,2C8.1,2,5,5.1,5,9c0,5.3,7,13,7,13s7-7.8,7-13C19,5.1,15.9,2,12,2z M12,11.5c-1.4,0-2.5-1.1-2.5-2.5s1.1-2.5,2.5-2.5s2.5,1.1,2.5,2.5S13.4,11.5,12,11.5z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Location:</strong> University of Rwanda Main Campus<br>
                                Nyagahinga, Kabuga, Rwanda
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                            <div style="color: #8e24aa; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 18px; min-width: 24px;">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#8e24aa">
                                    <path d="M20,4H4C2.9,4,2,4.9,2,6v12c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2h16c1.1,0,2-0.9,2-2V6C22,4.9,21.1,4,20,4z M20,18H4V8l8,5l8-5V18z M12,11L4,6h16L12,11z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <a href="<%= rsvpLink %>" style="display: block; width: 250px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9800, #f57c00); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; padding: 16px 0; text-align: center; border-radius: 50px; margin: 30px auto;">
                        Download Invitation
                    </a>

                    <h3 style="color: #7b1fa2; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Important Information</h3>
                    <ul style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>Please arrive at least 45 minutes before the ceremony begins</li>
                        <li>Graduates should report to the assembly area by 8:15 AM</li>
                        <li>Professional photography services will be available</li>
                        <li>A reception will follow the ceremony in the University Courtyard</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        We look forward to celebrating this special day with you and your family.
                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        Sincerely,<br>
                        <strong>Dr. Elizabeth Mbabazi</strong><br>
                        Dean of Students<br>
                        University of Rwanda
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
                <td style="background-color: #7b1fa2; color: #ecf0f1; padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0;">University of Rwanda &copy; 2025. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #e1bee7;">
                        For questions about the ceremony, contact:<br>
                        <a href="mailto:graduation@ur.ac.rw" style="color: #e1bee7;">graduation@ur.ac.rw</a> or call (250) 123-4567
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>